    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly 'as-is' for parts or as a major restoration project. The engine suffers from a severe oil leak and requires a complete rebuild, and the transmission is currently slipping significantly in second and third gears. The exterior shows extensive rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior upholstery is heavily torn and the electronics are non-functional. Buyer will need to arrange for a tow as it is not currently roadworthy.",
